Openclaw Docker本地部署(WINDOWS)
参考视频：https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Buw2zSEZ7/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_custom_collection.content.click  
感谢作者，作者Gethub参考为：https://github.com/Mo-Morris/bibi-share

1、环境检查：
Docker Desktop（windows x64） 下载地址：https://desktop.docker.com/win/main/amd64/Docker%20Desktop%20Installer.exe?utm_source=docker&utm_medium=webreferral&utm_campaign=dd-smartbutton&utm_location=module
WSL 2（Windows Subsystem for Linux 2）：gethub地址：https://github.com/microsoft/WSL/releases（wsl.2.7.1.0.x64.msi
）目前最新版本是2.7.1.0
git工具下载https://git-scm.com(安装包安装)


2、安装并初始化Openclaw：
安装Openclaw，进行初始化，skills和相关设置可以先不跳过，大模型我选择的是Coding Plan月付费模式
OpenClaw https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git（通过git工具来下载  命令是 git clone 地）
命令：git clone  https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw.git


3、创建并初始化Docker容器：

命令：OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_BIND=loopback ./docker-setup.sh

安装完毕后分别执行一下命令：

• 查询容器状态：docker compose ps

• .env文件修改命令：vim.evn   (修改loopback到lan)

• 跳过访问来源校验命令：docker compose -f docker-compose.yml run --rm openclaw-cli 
config set gateway.controlUi.allowedOrigins '["*"]' --strict-json

• 跳过设备校验命令：docker compose -f docker-compose.yml run --rm openclaw-cli 
config set gateway.controlUi.dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth true

• 网关安全校验降级命令：docker compose -f docker-compose.yml run --rm openclaw-cli 
config set gateway.controlUi.dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth true

• 地址：http://127.0.0.1:18789  登录需要输入Token，获取Token命令:cat .env
如果遇到登录报错，如：pairing required，可以输入如下命令：

docker compose run --rm openclaw-cli devices list# 批准设备
docker compose exec openclaw-gateway node dist/index.js devices approve <请求ID>

3、安装飞书插件：

 安装插件：docker compose -f docker-compose.yml run --rm openclaw-cli 
plugins install @openclaw/feishu

飞书配置机器人说明：https://docs.openclaw.ai/zh-CN/channels/feishu


说明：
1、文件路径，可以根据需要，cmd切换到D盘，如我设置的位置为D:\openclaw-docker\openclaw
2、Openclaw控制台中文界面位置在左侧菜单中的控制-概览-语言，改成中文






Openclaw Docker本地部署(威联通Docker)
参考视频：https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV13PAJzAECZ/?spm_id_from=333.1387.homepage.video_card.click&vd_source=c0fd5e7b846438f5f6cab642d2c57ffc
映像：docker.1ms.run/justlikemaki/openclaw-docker-cn-im:latest

注意：开启root权限

openclaw dashboard --no-open  
su node
进入后先切换到 node 用户

su node

Yaml程序代码如下：
version: '3.8'
x-openclaw-common-env: &openclaw-common-env
 TZ: Asia/Shanghai
 HOME: /home/node
 TERM: xterm-256color

 SYNC_OPENCLAW_CONFIG: "true"
 SYNC_MODEL_CONFIG: "true"
 MODEL_ID: "MiniMax-M2.7"
 PRIMARY_MODEL: "MiniMax-M2.7"
 IMAGE_MODEL_ID: ""
 BASE_URL: "https://api.minimaxi.com/v1"
 API_KEY: "密钥"
 API_PROTOCOL: "openai-completions"
 CONTEXT_WINDOW: "200000"
 MAX_TOKENS: "200000"
 DM_POLICY: "open"
 GROUP_POLICY: "open"
 ALLOW_FROM: "*"
 TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN: "密钥"
 TELEGRAM_DM_POLICY: "pairing"
 TELEGRAM_ALLOW_FROM: "账户数字id"
 TELEGRAM_GROUP_POLICY: "disabled"
 FEISHU_DEFAULT_ACCOUNT: "default"
 FEISHU_BOT_NAME: "OpenClaw Bot"
 FEISHU_REPLY_MODE: "auto"
 FEISHU_THREAD_SESSION: "true"
 FEISHU_OFFICIAL_PLUGIN_ENABLED: "false"
 FEISHU_STREAMING: "true"
 FEISHU_FOOTER_ELAPSED: "true"
 FEISHU_FOOTER_STATUS: "true"
 FEISHU_REQUIRE_MENTION: "true"
 DINGTALK_MESSAGE_TYPE: "markdown"
 DINGTALK_DEBUG: "false"
 DINGTALK_SHOW_THINKING: "false"
 DINGTALK_ASYNC_MODE: "false"
 WECOM_DEFAULT_ACCOUNT: "open"
 WECOM_COMMANDS_ENABLED: "true"
 WECOM_COMMANDS_ALLOWLIST: "/new,/compact,/help,/status"
 WECOM_ADMIN_USERS: "admin-userid"
 WECOM_DYNAMIC_AGENTS_ENABLED: "true"
 WECOM_DYNAMIC_AGENTS_ADMIN_BYPASS: "false"
 WECOM_SEND_THINKING_MESSAGE: "false"
 WECOM_DM_CREATE_AGENT_ON_FIRST_MESSAGE: "true"
 WECOM_GROUP_CHAT_ENABLED: "true"
 WECOM_GROUP_CHAT_REQUIRE_MENTION: "true"
 WECOM_GROUP_CHAT_MENTION_PATTERNS: "@"
 WORKSPACE: "/home/node/.openclaw"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN: "123456"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_BIND: "lan"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT: "18789"
 OPENCLAW_BRIDGE_PORT: "18790"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_MODE: "local"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_ALLOWED_ORIGINS: "http://192.168.100.138:18789,http://localhost"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_ALLOW_INSECURE_AUTH: "true"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_DANGEROUSLY_DISABLE_DEVICE_AUTH: "true"
 OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_AUTH_MODE: "token"
 OPENCLAW_PLUGINS_ENABLED: "true"
 OPENCLAW_TOOLS_JSON: '{"profile":"full","exec":{"host":"gateway","security":"full","ask":"off"}}'

services:

 openclaw-gateway:

  container_name: openclaw-gateway

  image: docker.1ms.run/justlikemaki/openclaw-docker-cn-im:latest

  cap_add:

   - CHOWN

   - SETUID

   - SETGID

   - DAC_OVERRIDE

  user: "0:0"

  environment: *openclaw-common-env

  volumes:

   - /share/Container/openclaw-nas/node:/home/node/.openclaw

   - /share/Container/openclaw-nas/node/openclaw-extensions:/home/node/.openclaw/extensions

  ports:

   - "18789:18789"

   - "18790:18790"

  init: true

  restart: unless-stopped

 openclaw-installer:

  container_name: openclaw-installer

  image: justlikemaki/openclaw-docker-cn-im:latest

  profiles:

   - tools

  user: "0:0"

  environment: *openclaw-common-env

  volumes:

   - /share/Container/openclaw-nas/node:/home/node/.openclaw

   - /share/Container/openclaw-nas/node/openclaw-extensions:/home/node/.openclaw/extensions

  entrypoint: ["tail", "-f", "/dev/null"]

  init: true

  restart: "no"

  ports: []

  stdin_open: true

  tty: true

  cap_add:

   - CHOWN

   - SETUID

   - SETGID

   - DAC_OVERRIDE


volumes:

 openclaw-extensions:


